    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small dining areas, usually extensions of kitchens or pantries; for such areas when they are extensions of living rooms, use "dining alcoves."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
